'''Solange Yijika''' ni umukinnyi wo muri cameroon ukomeye cyane  <ref>https://mobile.camerounweb.com/CameroonHomePage/entertainment/Top-Cameroonian-actress-Solange-Yijika-is-back-Photos-354613</ref> <ref>http://www.tiptopstars.com/mtdv/component/content/article/191-solange-yijika-a-step-forward.html</ref> <ref>https://mobile.camerounweb.com/CameroonHomePage/entertainment/Meet-5-most-talented-young-Cameroonian-actresses-344962</ref> <ref>https://www.tvovermind.com/casting-behold-dreamers-movie/</ref> <ref>http://www.dc-comm.com/cameroonian-movie-industry-brenda-shey-the-mother-hen/</ref> kandi agaragara cyane mu makinamico ya  Nigeria <ref name="So">https://lefilmcamerounais.com/2016/03/22/people-solange-yijika-lactrice-camerounaise-qui-sexporte/</ref> ni producer wa film, <ref>https://10times.com/atlanta-film-festival/visitors</ref> ndetse  uburenganzira uburenganzira bw'umugore n'umwana. <ref name="Fr">https://lefilmcamerounais.com/2016/04/26/5actwn-solange-yijika-actrice/</ref> Niwe mukinnyi w'amafirime uzwi cyane mu karere ka Afurika yo hagati akaba n'umuntu ukomeye mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Kameruni (CAMIFF). <ref name="Ach">https://lefilmcamerounais.com/2016/04/26/5actwn-solange-yijika-actrice/</ref>

