== Umwuga ==
Yijika yari isura ikomeye mubikorwa bya firime ya Kameruni kuva yagaragara bwa mbere nko mumwaka wa 2005. Mu byapa bibiri byo kurwanya malariya muri Kameruni byatewe inkunga na ''Global Fund yo kurwanya Malariya, Igituntu na SIDA'', yakoreshejwe nk'icyitegererezo muri ibyo byapa.  Ni n'umurwanashyaka uharanira ubutabera ku isi ku bagore n'abana. Yabaye ambasaderi ku nshuro ya 1 iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya Kameruni (CAMIFF) mu 2016. 

Yijika yari yagaragaye mu nganda za sinema zo muri Kameruni mu bicuruzwa byinshi bigera kuri 20 kandi ni we uhabwa ibihembo byinshi birimo ibihembo bya AMAA na NAFCA. <ref>https://cameroonpostline.com/anglophonecelebsshineat/</ref>

Yakinnye muri " ''Ibigeragezo Byifuzo'' " 2006 bya TV byerekanwe kuri CRTV, aho yakinnye nka "Diana". Nyuma yaje muri 2008 yagaragaye muri " ''Mark of the Absolute'' ", filime Asaba Ferdinand yayoboye akanayikora. Hakurikiraho " ''Igihugu'' Cy'igicucu" 2009, filime yakozwe na Agbor Gilbert Ebot ikayoborwa na Zack Orji na Neba Lawrence. Muri filime kandi hagaragayemo Jim Iyke . Muri uwo mwaka, yongeye kandi kugaragara muri filime " ''Ububabare bukomeye'' " iyobowe na Neba Lawrence, hanyuma, muri uwo mwaka agaragara muri " ''Royal Destiny'' ", filime yo muri Kameruni yanagaragayemo Emeka Ike na Tonto Dikeh, abakinnyi babiri ba Nollywood . Mu mwaka wa 2012, yagaragaye muri " ''Troubled Kingdom'' ", filime iyobowe na Neba Lawrence, ifatanije na producer wa firime ukomoka muri Amerika Mairo Sanda hamwe na [[Afurika y’Epfo|Fred Keyanti ukomoka muri Afurika y'Epfo]] - bashimye ubuhanga bw'uyu mukinnyi. 

Mu mwaka wa 2012, yakinnye muri filime ya Nollywood '', "Amaraso cyangwa Divayi'' ", yakozwe na Henry Neba Awantoh na Jim Iyke kandi iyobowe na Neba Lawrence, yanditswe na Ruth Kadiri . <ref>https://www.nollywoodreinvented.com/2013/05/blood-or-wine.html</ref>

Muri 2013, yatorewe ibihembo bya SONNAH. 

Yagaragaye muri filime, " ''Decoded'' ", yakozwe na Brenda Elung - nawe umukinnyi wa filime kandi iyobowe na Akim Macaulay na Enah Johnscott mu 2013, aho yakinnye hamwe [[Gana|nabakinnyi ba Gana]] na Kameruni nka Van Vicker, Jeffery Epule na Desmond Wyte. <ref>https://www.pulse.ng/gist/cameroon-movie-industry-critically-awaits-decoded-movie/bgn5r6g</ref>

Yabaye umwe mu bayobozi babiri baganiriye ku nama nyunguranabitekerezo mu mwaka wa 2016 mu birori byo gutanga ibihembo bya African Achievers Awards, byabereye ku ya 8 Nyakanga mu kigo mpuzamahanga cy’inama, [[Abuja]], muri [[Nijeriya]] hamwe na Richard Mofe Damijo, umukinnyi wa politiki akaba n'umunyapolitiki.  <ref>https://mobile.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/Lordina-Mahama-Agyepong-Sinach-Set-to-Receive-2016-African-Achievers-Awards-453641</ref>

Muri filime yo muri 2017, " ''Kugaragaza Ubutwari bwo Gukiza'' ", iyobowe na Musing Derick Tening kandi yakozwe na Tessy Eseme, yakinnye nka " ''Jazmine Juma'' ". <ref>https://m.imdb.com/title/tt6994278/fullcredits?ref_=m_ttfcd_tt</ref> Filime yerekanwe bwa mbere i Londres. <ref>https://www.designmynight.com/london/whats-on/film-screenings/expression-london-movie-premiere</ref> <ref>https://www.glamafrica.com/expression-movie-premieres-in-london-on-october-13-2017-get-more-details-here</ref>

Yatorewe igihembo mu nshuro ya 2 ya CAMIFF Awards, <ref>https://critiqsite.com/2017/02/04/vote-between-these-top-cameroonian-anglophone-actresses-who-will-steal-the-show-at-the-upcoming-camiff/</ref> yabaye hagati ya 24-29 Mata 2017 i Buea, muri [[Kameruni]] hamwe nabandi bakinnyi ba Camerwood na Nollywood nabo batowe. <ref>https://www.fabafriq.com/articles/on-the-highway-to-camiff-2017</ref> Yari umwe mu baterankunga ba CAMIFF 2018 hamwe na Ramsey Nouah wa Nollywood . <ref>https://www.cameroon-tribune.cm/article.html/18091/fr.html/cinema-cap-sur-le-camiff-2018</ref>

